t: "wdkhl alsijn mae yusif fatayan, qal ahdhma: 'iiniy ra'ayt fi almanam 'aniy 'aesir enbana lysyr khmrana, waqal alakhr: 'iiniy ra'ayt 'aniy 'ahmil fawq rasi khbzana takul altayr mnh, 'akhbarana -ya yusif -btfsyr ma rayna, 'iinaa narak min aladhin yuhsinun fi ebadthm llh, wmeamlthm lkhlqh"